* 4× [[20 mm caliber|20 mm (0.787 in)]] [[M61 Vulcan]] [[Gatling gun|6-barrel Gatling cannon]]

;AC-130A Surprise Package, Pave Pronto, AC-130E Pave Spectre
* 2× 7.62&nbsp;mm GAU-2/A miniguns
* 2× 20&nbsp;mm M61 Vulcan cannon
* 2× 40&nbsp;mm (1.58&nbsp;in) [[Bofors 40 mm gun|L/60 Bofors cannon]]

;AC-130E Pave Aegis
* 2× 20&nbsp;mm M61 Vulcan cannon
* 1× 40&nbsp;mm (1.58&nbsp;in) L/60 Bofors cannon
* 1× 105&nbsp;mm (4.13&nbsp;in) [[M102 howitzer]]

