* 1× 40&nbsp;mm (1.58&nbsp;in) L/60 Bofors cannon
* 1× 105&nbsp;mm (4.13&nbsp;in) M102 howitzer

;AC-130W Stinger II / AC-130J Ghostrider<ref name="ghostrider"/>
